% Purpose: Context card reviewer agent validating grounding and quality of generated cards

% Requirements
- Create Kafka consumer agent (ai.context_card_reviewer.v1)
- Validate ContextCard drafts from writer
- Use Ollama reviewer model to verify citation accuracy
- Check that all claims reference valid EvidenceUnit IDs with locators
- Assess coherence and completeness
- Suggest improvements
- Enforce mandatory grounding constraint: reject cards with ungrounded claims
- Publish approved cards to events.kb.v1 or revision requests to events.steps.requested.v1

% Output Format
- Generate Python module at src/agents/context_card_reviewer.py
- Include comprehensive type hints
- Use async/await patterns

